{"tid":1801652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動]好好利用31同1號既活動 唔好再留於行行企企","createTime":"2019-12-28T19:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T19:47:17.000Z","uid":302895,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0520f5d0cecb8375901a66cd5da0af9f86c2ba5","tid":1801652,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:37:35.000Z","msg":"我諗大家都認同罷工係和理非最終極武器<br />\n我知而家一直搞緊工會 但基數好似始終唔大<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>三罷channel而家連十萬人都仲未有</strong></span></span><br />\n所以我覺得宣傳力度要再加強<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁點先可以好好利用黎緊呢兩次活動呢？</span><br />\n先講31號人鏈 人鏈牽涉範圍甚廣 十八區都有 而且正值倒數時分 相信仲會有啲淺黃帶住一家大細出黎 人流應該都唔少<br />\n<br />\n具體做法：<br />\n1.都係一般做法 攞住罷工文宣 沿人鏈行 並叫人入channel<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.人鏈既優勢 印一堆文宣 唔洗太多 由你自己 向你右手面傳出去 入左channel既就傳 未入既就停一停 scan個QR code 再傳 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n再講元旦遊行<br />\n具體做法：<br />\n1.都係做反一直以黎做緊既野 邊行邊攞住文宣<br />\n2.我覺得有一個位可以稍稍改變既<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係唔想齋行 覺得無成效既 就企定定係一個位 不停叫人過黎入工會</span><br />\n如斯做法 一黎唔會出現要手足追住你黎scan既問題 二黎就係你會清楚見到有幾多人因為你而入工會 正能量gain<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢兩次活動 我想見到大量既罷工文宣 唔要只能觀賞既罷工文宣 要有埋工會QR code既文宣</span></strong></span><br />\n唔想淨係得警暴行為/其他 因為出得黎既 其實相信都無人唔知政府幾撚pk 當然你要做 我都唔反對<br />\n<br />\nbtw以上係比一啲平時乜都唔拎 齋出黎行行企企既和理非做既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">總之唔要見到你兩手空空呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一係攞遮 一係攞文宣同入公會呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">仲有 其實遊行人數而家真係唔洗太在意 因為比起以前 遊行危險左 有啲老弱婦孺 一家大細真係會變到唔敢出 或者係因為身體問題而無得出 但只要有人出黎 就代表仲有人在意 革命之火 仍然未滅 無降溫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">麻煩認同既話幫我推上熱門直至遊行完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我係P牌仔 我推唔郁 靠大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有更好建議歡迎提出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3a50237172925edd5dc1147899eaec07526deac1","tid":1801652,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:42:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0938a4870dd7ba724c7ff42fcce32406efc97bf9","tid":1801652,"uid":304597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T19:49:37.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁☹️幫推！"},{"pid":"990e9cee239b6e853a23df06f4491534d7a05b0b","tid":1801652,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1372ca618bd6669a23a2bdb01f3287ebeae3d791","tid":1801652,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T19:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5EerbM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5EerbM.jpg&h=3100a259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7oMgEwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7oMgEwN.jpg&h=b543d245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BrfECit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrfECit.jpg&h=e2e62638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可以印呢幾張 印幾張野帶出去姐 都唔係好難掛</strong></span></span>"}]}